      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HIS FERNANDO (7) is a quick beginner who bombed the start last time and missed the frame, finishing fifth (20.33) in a Grade 5 at this track. Hit the ground running and placed (20.33) at this track the start prior. Form at the trip sound including six wins. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Rates on top in this line up. ON APPEAL (8) filled a minor placing last start at Taree Super Track behind Kiarni Bolt (17.66) in a Grade 4/5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Expected to feature. SNIDELY WHIPLASH (2) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 340m behind DENAWEN BEACH (21.50) in a Grade 4/5. Placed at her previous run. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. SUNNYBROOK (3) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
